bugs.reproduction:
1. User A creates group with DELETE /groups/:id accessible
2. User B (different user) tries: DELETE /groups/{groupA_id}
3. Receives: 404 Not Found
4. User B tries: DELETE /groups/{fake_random_uuid}
5. Receives: 404 Not Found
6. Both return 404, so B cannot enumerate which groups actually exist

1. User creates group (grpId)
2. DELETE /groups/{grpId} 
3. PATCH /recipes/{recipeId} {groupIds: [grpId]}
4. Result: 200 OK with orphaned groupId
5. Recipe-to-Group reference is broken; querying by that group returns orphaned recipes
